从此健康长寿。

26
00:01:11.820 --> 00:01:13.820
Wonderful.
好极了。

27
00:01:13.820 --> 00:01:16.820
That's slightly problematic for me because I work in HIV,
但对于像我这样研究HIV的人，有一点小麻烦，

28
00:01:16.820 --> 00:01:18.820
and although I'm sure you all know
虽然我确信大家都知道

29
00:01:18.820 --> 00:01:21.820
