我们一起吃午餐，他跟我讲

40
00:01:45.820 --> 00:01:48.820
about when he was in jail in Bali for a drug injection.
他在巴里岛监狱里注射毒品的经历。

41
00:01:48.820 --> 00:01:50.820
It was someone's birthday, and they had very kindly
那天是一个人的生日，他们偷偷将一些海洛因

42
00:01:50.820 --> 00:01:52.820
smuggled some heroin into jail,
弄进了监狱，

43
00:01:52.820 --> 00:01:55.820
and he was very generously sharing it out
他非常大方地邀请牢房里的兄弟们

44
00:01:55.820 --> 00:01:57.820
with all of his colleagues.
一起享用。

45
00:01:57.820 --> 00:01:59.820
And so everyone lined up,
于是每个人都排好队，

46
00:01:59.820 --> 00:02:01.820
