所有瘾君子排成一排。

47
00:02:01.820 --> 00:02:03.820
and the guy whose birthday it was
过生日的那个人

48
00:02:03.820 --> 00:02:06.820
filled up the fit,
准备好注射器，

49
00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:08.820
and he went down and started injecting people.
蹲下身，开始给兄弟们注射海洛因。

50
00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:10.820
So he injects the first guy,
他给第一个兄弟注射后，

51
00:02:10.820 --> 00:02:13.820
and then he's wiping the needle on his shirt,
顺手用衣服擦擦针管，

52
00:02:13.820 --> 00:02:15.820
and he injects the next guy.
再注射下一个。

53
00:02:15.820 --> 00:02:19.820
And Frankie says, "I'm number 22 in line,
Frankie说：“我是第22个，

54
00:02:19.820 --> 00:02:22.820
and I can see the needle coming down towards me,
我看见针管离我越来越近，

55
00:02:22.820 --> 00:02:24.820
