地上到处都是血。

56
00:02:24.820 --> 00:02:26.820
It's getting blunter and blunter.
针管越来越钝。

57
00:02:26.820 --> 00:02:29.820
And a small part of my brain is thinking,
我脑子里在想，

58
00:02:29.820 --> 00:02:31.820
'That is so gross
“真是恶心死了

