故事讲完后，

65
00:02:43.820 --> 00:02:45.820
Frankie said,
Frankie说：

66
00:02:45.820 --> 00:02:47.820
"You know ... God,
“你知道，天，

67
00:02:47.820 --> 00:02:50.820
drugs really make you stupid."
毒品真能让你蠢到极点。”

68
00:02:51.820 --> 00:02:54.820
