"No, no. We share needles because we don't want to go to jail."
不是，不是。我们共用针头因为我们不想进监狱。”

107
00:04:22.820 --> 00:04:25.820
So, in Indonesia at this time,
现在，在印尼

108
00:04:25.820 --> 00:04:28.820
